      {
        "id": 282442,
        "name": "Elliot Smith",
        "username": "openthedoorhal",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/o/b3f665/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2026-01-09T17:20:53.261Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Meteor0id\" data-post=\"9\" data-topic=\"68978\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/meteor0id/48/55420_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Meteor0id:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Just want to drop here, love the passion shown for the correct labeling of a category.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Unfortunately, as you can see, some commenting on this thread seem to be passionately opposed to my vision of UX, indeed some of my arguments in this present discussion thread were even deleted.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Meteor0id\" data-post=\"9\" data-topic=\"68978\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/meteor0id/48/55420_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Meteor0id:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Maybe someone enjoys this little story of how Signal and this forum grew out to be.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Thank you, yes I appreciated your story; I think your comments here provide interesting context.  Ultimately, in technical design and implementation, we do need to consider many non-technical human factors, but strangely, very few of us consider ourselves to be sociotechnologists, instead we tend to take the non-technical aspects for granted.  Ultimately, the human factors seem to continue to be the most important in shaping the quality and character of Signal‚Äôs UI and UX.  Sam Bent seems to harbor something of an extremist right-wing crank perspective, but he does raise some generally plausible UX concerns in his recent Sep 11, 2025 video‚Ä¶  Oh well, at least we can all agree the leadership of Meredith Whittaker is still much preferable to that of Aamon Animations‚Äô ‚ÄúXelon Musk.‚Äù</p>",
